{"tid":1168438,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"哥帥去祖記？曼城急澄清","createTime":"2019-05-23T16:12:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T00:01:00.000Z","uid":7828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8466af4fd4b177da8da7cfac42c69d1b09d1e831","tid":1168438,"uid":7828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T16:12:22.000Z","msg":"對於哥迪奧拿轉投祖雲達斯執教的傳言，曼城方面澄清這是毫無根據的謠言。<br />\n<br />\n祖雲達斯教練柯歷利落實今夏離隊，令那支意甲班霸需尋覓新帥，外界更一度傳出帶領曼城贏得國內「3冠王」的主帥哥迪奧拿，將會轉戰意大利。<br />\n<br />\n對於外界的傳言，曼城董事會成員之一的艾拔圖加拉西（Alberto Galassi）在接受《天空體育》採訪時表示：「我想澄清過去幾天報道的內容，並確認哥迪奧拿上周在記者會內所說的內容，那就是他希望留在曼城。此外像祖雲達斯這樣的球會，是不會允許這種消息在曼城未被知會的情況下而出現。」<br />\n<br />\n加拉西續說：「這是毫無根據的謠言，傳媒追求這種謠言實在令人難以置信及太荒謬。我重申的是哥帥希望留在曼城，他不希望離隊，所以當中沒有任何問題出現，因為由始至終都沒有任何事發生。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/sports/player?newsId=sp25636655270\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Fsports%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3Dsp25636655270&d=jM2msIR27xdcbllsFNIWhEad0DqFW0GAicD%2BCHpJjC4%3D&h=1ac32a85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Fsports%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3Dsp25636655270&h=be563861\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/sports/player?newsId=sp25636655270</a>"},{"pid":"21a2fd67e9b5ce2b71aca7b605b0cbeb23a87be8","tid":1168438,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T16:56:56.000Z","msg":"謠言終結者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81cf9665585453dd2093388e8bd49819861ccafb","tid":1168438,"uid":3764,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T18:02:27.000Z","msg":"有無脷迷精彩留言睇返"},{"pid":"16b81f7dbef8181865843ea4d9e09aa564aff632","tid":1168438,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81cf9665585453dd2093388e8bd49819861ccafb","tid":1168438,"uid":3764,"like":1,"dislike":6